node_9.subject: Mina Chang
node_9.description: This is Mina Chang's plan for Monday February 13: 7:00 am - Wake up and complete morning routine, 8:00 am - Have breakfast with Iris and discuss weekend plans, 9:00 am - Attend morning classes at Oak Hill College, 12:00 pm - Have lunch in the dining hall and flirt with some classmates, 1:00 pm - Attend afternoon classes, participate actively in discussions, 3:00 pm - Hang out with friends in the student lounge, talk about the new guy, 4:00 pm - Meet up with Iris to plan how to approach the new male student, 5:00 pm - Prepare for dinner and freshen up for the evening, 6:00 pm - Have dinner with friends, and share laughs while subtly discussing the new guy, 7:00 pm - Join a study group session in the library, work on upcoming project, 8:30 pm - Head back to the dorm, play music and relax with Iris, 9:00 pm - Get ready for a social gathering in the common area, dress to impress, 10:00 pm - Attend the gathering, mingle and keep an eye on the new student, 11:00 pm - Wind down and chat with Iris about the day's events before going to bed..
